{"tid":1308550,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"阿根廷足協副主席：美斯如果冇證據 就得公開道歉","createTime":"2019-07-12T02:20:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T17:26:17.000Z","uid":43785,"like":68,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"194fedcc9a1765b383d9fe4cdc00c684b4439b9a","tid":1308550,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:20:50.000Z","msg":"在阿根廷0-2不敵巴西之後，梅西炮轟裁判不公，並暗示南美足聯要內定巴西奪冠。在決賽後，梅西又怒斥南美足協很腐敗。這兩番話，使得梅西遭到了巴西人的集體圍攻。如今阿根廷足協第三副主席拉德也表態稱，梅西如果沒證據，那就得進行公開道歉。<br />\n<a href=\"https://3g.163.com/sports/article/EJNBTO4G00058781.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F3g.163.com%2Fsports%2Farticle%2FEJNBTO4G00058781.html&d=tO8FO7ZpCqi602%2BiQgdm0Obr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=951e2d7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://3g.163.com/sports/article/EJNBTO4G00058781.html</a><br />\n連自己人都唔幫佢啦，點攪?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbb14a992679d0dfb3d30797b85a728d451112e2","tid":1308550,"uid":43785,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:23:04.000Z","msg":"道歉又好，唔道都好，<br />\n<br />\n我地全力支持美斯決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />維護美斯主權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拒絕外國勢力（巴西，智利等）干預美斯踢波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"3980b85d5c06dbfbd013b6c5e26e50c4577edbad","tid":1308550,"uid":43660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:24:26.000Z","msg":"Sorry Sir!"},{"pid":"d94ebd83574b542f8a954f6e06ed95700664a06c","tid":1308550,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:25:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span sty